ASSIGNMENT 2: Delivery Delay Impact on Profit
Business Question

Does delayed shipping reduce profitability?

 Step 1: Create Delivery Days Column
Delivery Days =
DATEDIFF(Orders[Order Date], Orders[Ship Date], DAY)
 Step 2: Create Delay Category
Delivery Status =
IF(Orders[Delivery Days] > 5, "Delayed", "On Time")
 Step 3: Create Profit Measure
Profit by Status = SUM(Orders[Profit])
 Step 4: Visual

======================================================

ASSIGNMENT 3: Discount Abuse Detection

Which customers receive high discount but give low profit?

Step 1: Measures
Avg Discount = AVERAGE(Orders[Discount])
Profit Margin =
DIVIDE([Total Profit], [Total Sales])
Step 2: Risk Condition
Discount Risk =
IF(
    [Avg Discount] > 0.3 &&
    [Profit Margin] < 0.1,
    "High Risk",
    "Safe"
)
 Step 3: Visual

Table:

Customer Name

Avg Discount

Profit Margin

Risk
